{
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_0100_10": "奇巴納！請照我們的計畫，\n切換成那個天氣啊！",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_0200_10": "勝負總是動盪翻騰！\n萬一我健忘了，你也別生氣啊！",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_0300_10": "咆哮吧！狂風！\n掀起猛烈的沙暴吧！",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_0400_10": "這樣一來就沒有任何東西能夠擊碎你！\n交給你了，巨炭山！",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_0500_10": "變成對手較有利的天氣了……！",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_0600_10": "………………",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_0700_10": "小優，我們先打倒\n沙漠蜻蜓吧。",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_0800_10": "因為掀起沙暴的是\n沙漠蜻蜓。",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_0900_10": "而且在經過一段時間後，\n沙暴就會平息。",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_1000_10": "我們要等待攻擊的機會。\n在那之前就由轟擂金剛猩來防守。",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_1100_10": "所以……",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_1200_10": "如果轟擂金剛猩倒下，\n巨炭山就交給妳對付了！",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_1300_10": "我明白了！",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_1400_10": "哦～你們好像\n玩得很開心呢。",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_1500_10": "呃！？美蓉……！",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_1600_10": "嗨～！奇巴納！\n最近還好嗎？",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_1700_10": "……麻煩的人來了。",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_1800_10": "也讓我們參加嘛。\n那樣訓練起來\n才更有效果吧？",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_1900_10": "是不是？露璃娜？",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_2000_10": "嗯，別把我們排除在外喔。",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_2100_10": "糟了！喂，小勝！\n你快加入我們！",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_2200_10": "情況緊急！\n請你助我們一臂之力！",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_2300_10": "那小優就跟我們一隊囉。\n就用帕希歐風格的\n３對３來對戰吧。",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_2400_10": "……小優妳也千萬要小心。",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_2500_10": "畢竟美蓉她對同伴\n也是毫不留情啊……",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_2600_10": "總覺得……",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/4001_1001_2700_10": "有得折騰了……",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/6801_1031_0100_10": "母子間的爭吵啊……",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/6801_1001_0100_10": "………………",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/6801_1001_0200_10": "………………",
    "episode_event_masaru_gordie_melon/6801_1001_0300_10": "哈哈哈……這問題看來不是\n第三者介入就能解決的呢。"
}
